+{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01Px9ZzgA1iXthQHUPcy7pbx","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# T4: Phantom Invoice Bug\n     2→\n     3→**Category:** bugfix/medium\n     4→**Timeout:** 30 minutes\n     5→**Diff limit:** 20 changed lines in `src/`\n     6→\n     7→## Description\n     8→\n     9→An invoicing microservice has several failing tests. Your job is to find and fix the bugs so that all tests pass.\n    10→\n    11→Run `npm test` to see the current failures. There are 30 visible tests — 4 are currently failing. There is also a hidden regression test suite with 10 tests. Your fix must not break any passing tests.\n    12→\n    13→### Constraints\n    14→\n    15→- Your changes to `src/` must be at most 20 lines (added + removed), enforced by `tests/diff-size.test.ts`.\n    16→- Do not modify any test files.\n    17→- `npm run build` and `npm run lint` must continue to pass.\n    18→\n    19→### Hints\n    20→\n    21→- The bugs are in the service/query layer, not in the test expectations.\n    22→- Read the failing test names carefully — they describe the expected behavior.\n    23→- Not every TODO comment or suspicious-looking function is actually a bug that needs fixing.\n    24→\n    25→## Getting Started\n    26→\n    27→```bash\n    28→npm install\n    29→npm test        # See which tests fail\n    30→npm run build   # Verify TypeScript compiles\n    31→npm run lint    # Verify lint passes\n    32→```\n    33→\n    34→## Validation\n    35→\n    36→All 30 visible tests + 10 hidden regression tests must pass. The diff constraint test must also pass.\n    37→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01VSDbtP63uuag1N2gHWBMAc","session_id":"7116ff12-be08-47c8-904c-6ac30dd36b6c","uuid":"d5944456-1245-4cca-b5ca-8965ee976b5e"}
